    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power unit delivers 414 hp with a linear power band peaking at 8,300 RPM, mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from the Variable M Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for exceptional lateral grip and turn-in response. Meticulously maintained with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The hydraulic steering rack offers communicative feedback often lost in newer iterations. A mechanically sound example of the last atmospheric V8 M-car, ready for spirited B-road sessions or track duty.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
